                            <comment id="13660784" author="cheolsoo" created="Fri, 17 May 2013 16:19:24 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I am giving my +1 because this makes code much cleaner.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I haven&apos;t done any performance benchmarks because I agree with Julien&apos;s assessment. But please advise if anyone has concerns.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
